request URL: protocol://location/path/file.ext

input/output (TODO: Use libcurl if available)
----------------------------------------------
  * io
    + file
      - file open/close
      - file descriptor read/write
      * extension
    + http
      - socket open/close
      - file descriptor read/write
      * extension


file extension
----------------------------------------------
  * extension
    + wav (container format)
      - handle container header
      * format
    + mp3
      * format (mp3)
  ( + ogg (vorbis/speex) )
  ( + flac (flac) )


data format
----------------------------------------------
  * format
    + pcm
      - big/little endian
      - floats
      - compressed
      - integer
        - signed/unsigned 
    + mp3
      - raw
  ( + vorbis )
  ( + speex )
  ( + flac )

